  <prompt>Implement `ScheduledJobHost : BackgroundService` per spec.md design snippet: reads `sprk_backgroundjob` rows on startup + refreshes hourly; for each enabled job, parses cron via Cronos and manages a per-job `PeriodicTimer`; invokes `IScheduledJob.ExecuteAsync`; writes `sprk_backgroundjobrun` row per execution.</prompt>
  <goal>Host starts → enumerates registered IScheduledJob impls + Dataverse job rows → dispatches on schedule → records runs. Cancellation propagates within 30s (NFR-07).</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-001">In-process BackgroundService; no Azure Functions</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-010">DI minimalism — register as Singleton via AddHostedService</constraint>
    <constraint source="NFR-07">Honor CancellationToken throughout; host cancellation propagates within 30s</constraint>
    <constraint source="NFR-08">Every run carries correlationId</constraint>
  </constraints>
  <knowledge>
    <topic>background-service-cron-dispatch</topic>
